  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Actively seek out new sales opportunities through cold calling, site visit & networking</li><li>Secure new projects from existing client / new clients</li><li>Monitor upcoming and ongoing projects for tendering</li><li>Monitors and follow up long overdue payments </li><li>Regular Site or office visit</li><li>Achieve monthly sales target</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li>Act as focal point of contact between customers and internal staff</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum O levels / diploma</li><li>Minimum 2 year experience in outdoor sales</li><li>Persuasive and goal oriented</li><li>Aggressive and possess strong passion for sales</li><li>Experience in construction industry / materials will be an advantage</li><li>Right attitude and willing to learn</li><li>Possess own transport</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Basic Salary</strong></li><li><strong>Sales Target commission</strong></li><li><strong>Car Allowance</strong></li><li><strong>Medical Benefits</strong></li><li><strong>5 Days working week</strong></li></ul>",
